{"id": "art-25173", "label": "Art. 25173", "title": "Art. 25173", "slug": "art-25173", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_935469564\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1248\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_935469564\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>73</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1367225260\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1247\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1367225260\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Competen&#355;a</span> de verificare\na <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span> diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere sub aspectul procedurii pe care o urmeaz&#259; societatea\npersoan&#259; juridic&#259; român&#259; care se divizeaz&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span> registratorului de la oficiul registrului <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> în a c&#259;rui raz&#259; teritorial&#259;\neste situat sediul social al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nPrevederile art. 105 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span style='color:black'> se aplic&#259;\nîn mod corespunz&#259;tor. În scopul exercit&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>competen&#355;ei</span>\nde verificare a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span> diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere, registratorul consult&#259; <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;iile</span>\npublice competente, inclusiv, dac&#259; este cazul, pe cele din statul membru\nde <span class=SpellE>destina&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1728042473\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1246\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1728042473\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Societatea\ndepune, potrivit prevederilor art. 84 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nnr. </b></span><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\no cerere de eliberare a certificatului prealabil diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere, <span class=SpellE>înso&#355;it&#259;</span> de\nurm&#259;toarele:</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_408961753\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1245\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_408961753\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)proiectul de divizare transfrontalier&#259;, în forma\naprobat&#259; de adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_801564734\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1244\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_801564734\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)raportul administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, al\nmembrilor directoratului, la care se anexeaz&#259;, dac&#259; este cazul, <span\nclass=SpellE>observa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cele ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau creditorilor cu privire la proiectul de\ndivizare transfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259;\neste cazul, opinia <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde raportul prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>64</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, acordul <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> cu privire la\n<span class=SpellE>renun&#355;area</span> întocmirii raportului <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau dovezi care s&#259; ateste îndeplinirea <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>64</sup>\nalin. (3) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau (5);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1320457578\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1243\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1320457578\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)raportul expertului independent prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>65</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_328502667\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1242\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_328502667\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale privind aprobarea\ndiviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_615364165\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1241\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_615364165\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span>\nprivind îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale\nreferitoare la participarea <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la alte <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nde implicare a acestora, inclusiv, dac&#259; este cazul, privind începerea\nprocedurii de negociere, potrivit prevederilor Hot&#259;rârii Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>187/2007</span><span style='color:black'>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu privire la num&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>\nla momentul întocmirii proiectului de divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1879423848\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1240\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1879423848\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span> potrivit proiectului de divizare sau ca\nurmare a notific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> de\nc&#259;tre creditori, potrivit prevederilor art. 251<sup>71</sup> alin. (1),\nsau, dac&#259; este cazul, potrivit hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\nasupra cererii creditorilor, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nhot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2044344624\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1239\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2044344624\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>\ndisponibilului pentru plata, în termenul legal, a <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social ale <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> care <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>-au\nexercitat dreptul de retragere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259;\neste cazul, a <span class=SpellE>compensa&#355;iei</span> <span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span>\nstabilite prin hot&#259;râre judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1421885895\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1238\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1421885895\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)dac&#259; a fost introdus&#259; o cerere în anularea sau\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de aprobare\na diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere, hot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259; prin\ncare este respins&#259; cererea, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1338420672\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1237\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1338420672\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)<span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> pe propria\nr&#259;spundere a administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, a membrilor\ndirectoratului prin care confirm&#259; c&#259;, potrivit datelor <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nverific&#259;rilor efectuate în baza principiului <span class=SpellE>pruden&#355;ei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>diligen&#355;ei</span>\nbunului administrator, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259;\na <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nmodul de alocare a activelor la <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, în cazul unei diviz&#259;ri <span\nclass=SpellE>par&#355;iale</span>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la\nsocietatea ce face obiectul diviz&#259;rii, la data <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;iei</span>,\nasigur&#259; executarea <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> creditori decurgând din divizarea\ntransfrontalier&#259;, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>69</sup>-251<sup>71</sup>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_403710663\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1236\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_403710663\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registrul\noficiului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span>\ndin registrele <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span> de acesta <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de la alte <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ii</span>\npublice, pe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>, pe\nbaz&#259; de protocol dac&#259; este cazul, în scopul verific&#259;rii de\nc&#259;tre registrator a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndiviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere, urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_662250240\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1235\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_662250240\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)certificatul de atestare fiscal&#259;, care s&#259;\nateste executarea <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> c&#259;tre bugetul de stat <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> bugetele locale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_721484257\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1234\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_721484257\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din cazierul\nfiscal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1095377446\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1233\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1095377446\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din cazierul\njudiciar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1763246834\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1232\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1763246834\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din sistemul\ninformatic <span class=SpellE>na&#355;ional</span> integrat de <span\nclass=SpellE>eviden&#355;&#259;</span> a <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;elor</span>\nprovenite din <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span> - ROARMIS;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_298237308\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1231\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_298237308\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de filiale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> amplasarea\ngeografic&#259; a acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1357317762\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1230\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1357317762\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1100444003\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1229\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1100444003\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunile</span> <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;ionale</span>\naplicate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 53 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n54 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2005</span><span style='color:black'>,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 9 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n10 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>467/2006</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1302587919\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1228\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1302587919\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din registrul\nbeneficiarilor reali privind beneficiarii reali ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1211191786\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1227\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1211191786\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dac&#259; procedurile de derulare a diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprivind aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> nu sunt\nfinalizate ori dac&#259; nu sunt depuse toate înscrisurile prev&#259;zute de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, registratorul, prin încheiere, în\ntermen de 10 zile de la depunerea cererii, acord&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nun termen pentru regularizare, care nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\n15 zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2023016924\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1226\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2023016924\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dac&#259; procedurile de derulare a diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprivind aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> sunt îndeplinite\npotrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, iar rapoartele\nprev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>64</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>65</sup>\nsunt întocmite potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>,\nregistratorul emite certificatul prealabil diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere, al\nc&#259;rui format se aprob&#259; prin ordin al ministrului <span class=SpellE>justi&#355;iei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_391017557\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1225\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_391017557\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registratorul\nrespinge, motivat, cererea de emitere a certificatului prealabil diviz&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_422660520\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1224\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_422660520\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dac&#259; nu au fost îndeplinite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span>\nlegale privind divizarea transfrontalier&#259;, inclusiv în ceea ce <span\nclass=SpellE>prive&#351;te</span> întocmirea rapoartelor prev&#259;zute la art.\n251<sup>64</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>65</sup> potrivit <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau\nnu au fost depuse înscrisurile ce atest&#259; îndeplinirea acestor <span\nclass=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span> legale în termenul acordat de registrator;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_21482404\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1223\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_21482404\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul în care societatea care face obiectul\ndiviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere a fost condamnat&#259; definitiv pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irea</span> unei <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>,\niar pedeapsa amenzii sau, dup&#259; caz, cea complementar&#259; nu a fost\nînc&#259; executat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1192513088\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1222\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1192513088\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Dac&#259; din înscrisurile depuse de societate, din <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nînscrisurile aflate în dosarul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nde la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> sau din\ncele <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span> de registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\npe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span> rezult&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> unor indicii serioase c&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> transfrontalier&#259; se efectueaz&#259;\nîn scopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span class=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; duc&#259; la evaziune sau la eludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene sau a\ncelui intern ori în scopul <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>, registratorul sesizeaz&#259; tribunalul\nîn a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span> se afl&#259;\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, pentru a se <span\nclass=SpellE>pronun&#355;a</span> asupra cererii de emitere a certificatului\nprealabil diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere. În acest caz, toate înscrisurile\ndepuse de societate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> toate cele <span\nclass=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span>, pe cale <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ional&#259;</span>,\nde oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span>\nrelevante din registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> din registrul beneficiarilor reali sunt înaintate <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\ncompetente.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_37475478\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1221\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_37475478\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Cererea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (7) este <span\nclass=SpellE>solu&#355;ionat&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu prec&#259;dere, în camera de consiliu, cu\ncitarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. Pentru termenul fixat\nva fi citat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> parchetul de pe lâng&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> sesizat&#259;, c&#259;ruia i se vor comunica,\nîn copie, înscrisurile din dosar. În acest caz, punerea concluziilor de\nc&#259;tre procuror este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_976792840\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1220\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_976792840\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin hot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;at&#259;</span>,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 527-540 din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>134/2010</span><span style='color:black'> privind </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul de procedur&#259; civil&#259;</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, dac&#259;\nconstat&#259; îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale\npentru realizarea diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\nadmite cererea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dispune emiterea de c&#259;tre\nregistrator a certificatului prealabil diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere. În\ncazul în care constat&#259; c&#259; fuziunea transfrontalier&#259; se\nefectueaz&#259; în scopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span\nclass=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span> s&#259; duc&#259; la înc&#259;lcarea sau\nla eludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene sau a celui intern ori în scopul <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> de <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> respinge cererea de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere. Hot&#259;rârea <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este executorie <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\neste supus&#259; numai apelului, care poate fi exercitat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde Ministerul Public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1178921251\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1219\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1178921251\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Termenul de evaluare a cererii de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil diviz&#259;rii transfrontaliere nu poate <span\nclass=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span> 3 luni de la data depunerii cererii, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului prev&#259;zut la alin. (7), când\nacesta poate fi prelungit cu cel mult 3 luni. Dac&#259;, din cauza <span\nclass=SpellE>complexit&#259;&#355;ii</span> procedurii transfrontaliere sunt\nnecesare <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> sau verific&#259;ri\nsuplimentare, iar evaluarea nu poate fi realizat&#259; în aceste termene,\nregistratorul, din oficiu sau, dup&#259; caz, sesizat de <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;&#259;</span>,\ncomunic&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> motivele eventualelor\nîntârzieri, înainte de expirarea termenelor.</span></p>"}